Section 1:
Act 92 of the Regular Session
1 State of Arkansas
A Bill
2 95th General Assembly
3 Regular Session, 2025 HOUSE BILL 1393
4
5 By: Joint Budget Committee
6
7
For An Act To Be Entitled
8
9 AN ACT TO REAPPROPRIATE THE BALANCES OF CAPITAL
10 IMPROVEMENT APPROPRIATIONS FOR THE INSTITUTIONS OF
11 HIGHER EDUCATION; AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
12
13
Subtitle
14
15 AN ACT FOR THE INSTITUTIONS OF HIGHER
16 EDUCATION REAPPROPRIATION.
17
18
19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
20
21 SECTION 1. REAPPROPRIATION - ARKANSAS NORTHEASTERN COLLEGE. There is
22 hereby appropriated, to the Arkansas Northeastern College, to be payable from
23 the Development and Enhancement Fund, for the Arkansas Northeastern College
24 the following:
25 (A) Effective July 1, 2025, the balance of the appropriation provided
26 in Item (A) of Section 1 of Act 80 of 2024, for costs of construction of a
27 Precision Machining Facility, in a sum not to exceed .............$2,650,000.
28 (B) Effective July 1, 2025, the balance of the appropriation provided
29 in Item (B) of Section 1 of Act 80 of 2024, for technology upgrades for
30 Multi-Modal Course Delivery, in a sum not to exceed ................$850,000.
31 (C) Effective July 1, 2025, the balance of the appropriation provided
32 in Item (C) of Section 1 of Act 80 of 2024, for critical maintenance, in a
33 sum not to exceed ..................................................$320,000.
34 (D) Effective July 1, 2025, the balance of the appropriation provided
35 in Item (D) of Section 1 of Act 80 of 2024, for deferred maintenance, in a
36 sum not to exceed ..................................................$420,000.
